<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-the-benefits-go-beyond-looks">The benefits go beyond looks</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Wood lockers do more than just upgrade your locker room style. They also work as a powerful recruiting tool. Coaches tell us that showcasing a new locker room often helps secure top athletes.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
